1992;;Turtle Beach;;Australian;;Stephen Wallace;;Greta Scacchi, Joan Chen, Jack Thompson;;drama / thriller;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Turtle_Beach_(film);;Judith, an Australian photojournalist (Greta Scacchi), leaves her family to cover the story of Vietnamese boat people in a Malaysian refugee camp. There she befriends Minou, a Vietnamese streetwalker (Joan Chen), who has married a diplomat and together they try to bring awareness to the terrible conditions suffered by the people there.